Achieve design availability of Production, Utility and Safety Systems through effective coordination and control of maintenance and inspection systems, within planned budgets ;                                                                                                                                                    • Provide effective leadership to field maintenance team for safe and smooth functioning of all maintenance activities;  Managing team of 30-40 employees included Engineers and 50-60 contractors;                                                                                                                                                                                                • To lead the maintenance planning functions (SAP);                                                                                                • Coordination and control of maintenance and inspection ;                                                                                    • Lead the shutdown planning and act as focal point for all preparations, coordination and on schedule execution of tasks during shutdown;                                                                                                                                                            • To implement the maintenance philosophy, i.e. RCM,TPM;                                                                                       • Specifying consumables and spares part stock levels ;                                                                                             • Develop and maintain work patterns and personnel recourse planning ;                                                                 • To ensure that HSEQ system requirement are fully met;                                                                                    • Coordination of maintenance contractors and consultant services;                                                                         • Monitor & report personnel performance and competency;                                                                                                    • Prepare and execute development plans for maintenance staff;                                                                           • Fulfill role in Emergency response Team;                                                                                                                         • Participate and lead the safety audits, HAZOP, HAZIP etc.                                                         • Taking part in the selection, specification and procurement of equipment and other assets; 
• Carrying out work assignments to the highest quality level in accordance with policies, roles and responsibilities; 
Achievements:                                                                                                                           • Team leader for implementation of Process safety at OMV Petrom Kazakhstan. 
• Technical coordination and advising of the Project of «Gas piston power plant of 2х1819 kW electrical power». Project cost is 3.5 million $. Project is ongoing.               
•Maintenance Team Leader during of installation, commissioning, and startup of ESP pumps in all flowing wells in the field. Project cost is 3 million $.                                                                                            • Lead of project for upgrade pumping facility and installation, commissioning, and startup of new three MSD 3x6x9E, 14 Stage Crude Export Pumps by SULZER. Cost is 2.5 million $.                                                                                                                                   • Responsible and Technical adviser of Project “Process of Automatization of wells” Project cost is 1.5 million $. Project is ongoing.                                                                                      • Responsible for Develop & Implementation of Maintenance Management system TPM and RCM, Maintenance Procedures & Philosophy, Working Instructions, JD’s and etc. for Maintenance Department. Build and fulfill of and collection of data for CMMS (SAP).
